    • Uses of IAudioManager in sage.audio

      Classes in sage.audio that implement IAudioManager 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AudioManager
      This class acts as the abstract base class from which all concrete Audio Managers are derived.
      Methods in sage.audio that return IAudioManager 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      static IAudioManager AudioManagerFactory.createAudioManager(java.lang.String audioMgrClassName)
      A factory method (see the Factory Design Pattern) for creating instances of a particular AudioManager (that is, an object which implements the IAudioManager interface.
      Methods in sage.audio with parameters of type IAudioManager 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description

      Releases the sound back to memory.

    • Uses of IAudioManager in sage.audio.joal

      Classes in sage.audio.joal that implement IAudioManager 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  JOALAudioManager
      This class extends the AudioManager abstract class and uses the JOAL Java interface to OpenAL (http://jogamp.org) to provide a JOAL-based audio manager.
